From 11fba3b301db771574df357493ede231b5a0ac92 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Alok Singh <aloksing@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Fri, 27 Jun 2025 19:33:48 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] UPSTREAM: DP: wifi: ath12k: Enable word mask subscription for
 monitor TLV's

TLV compaction is not enabled in existing monitor implementation
and both qcn9274 and wcn7850 are using same TLV structures.

To improve CPU utilization on qcn9274, enable word mask support
for monitor TLVs.
Add word mask and compact TLV struct for the below TLVs.
1. MPDU_START
2. MPDU_END
3. MSDU_END
4. PPDU_END_USER_STATS

word mask subscription is at qword level, in compact tlvs
we enable only the qwords of interest and mask is generated accordingly.

Patch-dependency:
	0405-0010-UPSTREAM-DP-wifi-ath12k-Add-dynamic-configuration-su.patch

Signed-off-by: Alok Singh <aloksing@qti.qualcomm.com>
